Documentation of the game of Ships

Program is divided into individual packages that
ensures that the game logic and game play are independent.

The packages come with abstract classes that shows
the base schema that needs to be followed if further expansion
is wanted.

This isn't true for package Game that comes just with game logic
and package Util that only wraps Classes providing the schema for
communication between other packages.

Packages
Package
Description
org.chudoba.michal.zapoctak
Whole game wrapped into package.
org.chudoba.michal.zapoctak.AI
Package defining all needed function for usable AI.
org.chudoba.michal.zapoctak.Game
Package with logistic of the game.
org.chudoba.michal.zapoctak.Interface
Package defining how interface should work.
org.chudoba.michal.zapoctak.Util
Group of Classes with general use in the program.
